Package edu.rpi.legup.model.elements

Class Element

java.lang.Object
edu.rpi.legup.model.elements.Element
Direct Known Subclasses:
PlaceableElement
public abstract class Element extends Object
The Element class serves as an abstract base class for various elements used in the system. It handles basic properties such as ID, name, description, and image associated with the element.
